^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Again this hand illustrates that it is important on both offense and defense to count out the suits. Once I show up with one heart, Noi should realize Pam started with two and file that away in case it is important. And Pam should realize, because I opened 2D, Noi started with 2 diamonds. Sometimes this information makes no difference, but often it does, and if you get in the habit of automatically filing these things in your head, it really helps.|
