NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The other thing I want to comment on is Pam's ruffing of a diamond at trick 2. In this case, her plan is to set up dummy. There really is no reason to ruff diamonds, because the long trumps are in dummy. So, assuming hearts break, she can count six hearts, 1 spade, 1 diamond, and 1 club for sure.|
