NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now back to the plan. If hearts break, she needs one extra trick in the black suits. If Noi, has the Q of clubs, that is one possibility. However, once hearts don't break, she needs two extra tricks--needs an extra spade. And the easiest thing to do is play me for the K of spades. So lead a low spade towards the Q. But when that doesn't work, then you have to hope Noi also has the J of spades, so lead low towards your A10, Therefore, playing the 10 of spades right away was incorrect, because it took away one of your options. The idea is to keep as many options open as possible.|
