^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|OK, mostly I want to discuss the bidding, but let me make a brief comment about how best to play the heart suit. Basically, the easiest way to play the suit is to hope Betty has the K of hearts. if that is true, you lose one heart. So, the best play is low to the A and low back towards the Q. In this case there happens to be another unlikely distribution that means you only lose one heart trick as well. Because, Betty has J10 doubleton, your 9 sets up. an added bonus :) The reason to play the heart suit as I suggested is that it is your best hope for only one heart loser if Betty has the King.|
